name: Tatnall Kennedy
coverLetter: I am moving with my family up to Humboldt so my wife can be closer to her family in Mckinleyville, I need work so I can put a deposit down on a rental next month.  I am currently living in my travel trailer in Willow Creek while I go back and forth between tahoe and humboldt.  I am 39 years old and have been a bartender and restuarant server in lake tahoe for the past 15 years.  I am honest and trustworthy I just need a quick job for a month while I figure things out.;
